Subject line goes here
    - Capitalize subject line (as shown above)
    - Limit to 50 characters
    - Do not end line with period
    - Use imperative mood i.e. it should read like:
        If applied, this commit will <subject line>
<leave single blank line between subject line and body>
Body goes here
    - Body should explain what and why NOT how.
    - Body not necessary for very simple commits, subject might be enough.
    - Wrap at 72 characters.
